Well, I saw this tweet recently.

17
00:00:52,520 --> 00:00:54,520
And I really love it.

18
00:00:54,520 --> 00:00:58,640
Because I have spent many years as part of this Python community without really thinking

19
00:00:58,640 --> 00:01:00,640
about how things run.

